            <p>
                Communication is absolutely vital. Good communcation and communication skills can allow
                for more efficient work and significantly decreases the chances of misunderstandings. Communication bewteen co-workers can make the difference
                bewteen a job well done and being fired. Active listening is a the receiving portion of communication and is equally important. Both skills
                can be practiced frequently with teammates in team-based video games.
                <a href=""><strong>Learn more</strong></a>
            </p>
