            <h3>Teamwork/Collaboration</h3>
            <p>
                Teamwork and collaboration are needed in every situation and every scenario involving teams. Without teamwork and collaboration, teammates
                are more likely to be a burden than a help. Good teamwork can make tasks be accomplished faster, easier, and more accurately while poor teamwork
                can cripple a team. Teamwork skills can be practiced in video games as practice makes perfect and team-based video games provide perfect practice.
                <a href=""><strong>Learn more</strong></a>
            </p>
